original_title: Les Mills Combat - Shock Plyo HIIT 2
overview: Les Mills' Combat, Shock Plyo HIIT 2 is most challenging.  It's non-stop cardio and, even though it lasts for just under 30 minutes, it's the most difficult of the workouts to get through.  Your legs will burn!
title: Les Mills Combat - Shock Plyo HIIT 2
